text = "CO-OP CARD BRAWL — two eggs share one deck but spend their OWN energy. The pause stages the next wave's foes: pick a card, then choose WHERE it lands — weapons/abilities attach to one of your eggs, soldiers slot in beside an egg you control. Abilities last ONLY for that wave: cast from your ability bar (P1 keys 1–4, aim+click targeted ones; P2 gamepad buttons). Selected cards stay in hand; click to unselect. End Turn runs a 3-2-1, then the 15s wave. Lose only when BOTH eggs fall."
horizontal_alignment = 1
theme_override_colors/font_color = Color(0.92, 0.88, 0.72, 1)
theme_override_font_sizes/font_size = 16
